title: 047: How to meet women & embarrassing experiences
description: Every week MindPump receives dozens of listener questions on Instagram (@mindpump). Most of them are fitness related, however, some of them are not. In this episode, Sal, Adam & Justin take on a couple of these non-fitness related topics. Sal and Justin pump Adam about his well-tested female attracting strategy, then all three share embarrassing non-gym moments.
